xyz.fsgik.common.convert

接口 FsConverter


  • @ThreadSafe
public interface FsConverter
    Converter to convert object from source type to target type.

    A FsConverter consists of a list of FsConverter.Handlers and a set of FsConverter.Options. The handlers are composed of a prefix handler (maybe null), a list of middle handlers, and a suffix handler (maybe null).

    The conversion is performed in the order of 

         prefix handler (if not null) -> middle handlers -> suffix converter (if not null)
    More detail of conversion process, see FsConverter.Handler.convert(Object, Type, Type, FsConverter).
    另请参阅:
    FsConverter.Handler.convert(Object, Type, Type, FsConverter)

        static FsConverter defaultConverter()
        Returns default converter, of which handlers are:
        • Prefix handler: ReuseConvertHandler;
        • Suffix handler: BeanConvertHandler;
        • Common handlers:
          • EnumConvertHandler;
          • DateConvertHandler;
          • BytesConvertHandler;
          • BooleanConvertHandler;
          • NumberConvertHandler;
          • StringConvertHandler;
          • CollectConvertHandler;
        Those are constructed from empty constructor and in the order listed.

        default converter

      • convertType

        @Nullable
default @Nullable java.lang.Object convertType(@Nullable
                                                          @Nullable java.lang.Object source,
                                                          java.lang.reflect.Type sourceType,
                                                          java.lang.reflect.Type targetType)
        Converts source object from source type to target type. The result of this method in 3 types: null, FsWrapper and others:
        • null: means this converter can not do this conversion;
        • FsWrapper: wrapped object (from FsWrapper.get()) is actual result of conversion, including null and FsWrapper itself;
        • Others: any other type of returned object is the actual result of conversion.
        Using getResult(Object) can get actual result object from wrapper.
        参数:
        source - source object
        sourceType - source type
        targetType - target type
        返回:
        converted object or null

      • asHandler

        FsConverter.Handler asHandler()
        Returns this converter as FsConverter.Handler. For method FsConverter.Handler.convert(Object, Type, Type, FsConverter) of result handler, the 4th parameter FsConverter can be passed as null, in which case the 4th parameter will be auto passed with "this" -- the current converter itself.
